import React, { useState } from "react"; import { Select, Divider, Collapse, Form, Button, Row, Col, Card, Input, DatePicker, TimePicker } from 'antd'; import { PlusOutlined, MinusCircleOutlined } from "@ant-design/icons"; import { useSelector } from "react-redux"; import { useHistory } from "react-router"; import ConfirmationModal from "components/Modal/ConfirmationModal"; export default function TrackingSheet() { const { Option } = Select; const { Panel } = Collapse; const { TextArea } = Input; const history = useHistory(); const project = useSelector(state => state.authReducer.userProject); const initialProppantFormValues = { proppantData: [{ description: null, specific_gravity: null, bulk_density: null }] } const [items, setItems] = useState(['Stage 1']); const [showConfirmationModal, setShowConfirmationModal] = useState(); const [modalData, setModalData] = useState(); const handleCancel = () => { setShowConfirmationModal(false); setModalData(null); } const addStage = () => { setShowConfirmationModal(true); } const handleAddStageConfirmed = (data) => { addItem(); setShowConfirmationModal(false); setModalData(null); } const onFormSubmit = (values) => { console.log(values); }; const onDateChange = (date, dateString) => { console.log(date, dateString); } const showAddItemModal = () => { } const addItem = () => { setItems([...items, `Stage ${items.length + 1} (Added)`]) }; useState(() => { const wellId = history.location.pathname.split("/admin/")[1].split("/")[1]; const well = project.wellInfoValues.find(well => well.id == wellId); console.log(well); const stages = []; for (let step = 1; step <= well.no_of_stages; step++) { stages.push("Stage " + step); } setItems(stages); }, []) return ( <>
